Dialogs.Dialog: Want me to say "don't leave me", right？
Well, then, it's time to go.
Hey. We've arrived at our destination！
Haha, you're in a good mood.
Hey, have we arrived at our destination？
It was fun. I don't want to go home...
We have no choice. Let's go home.
Oh no. I can't believe it's already that late...
I see.. Too bad we have to leave.
I feel sorry for leaving, but shall we go home now？
Yes. I don't want to be too late.
Ah, we have to go home now.
It's trues. It's a good time.
Hey, don't you think it's time to go home？
Oh, really. Let's go home then.
What are you going to do now？ As a boyfriend.
Now, here's the crucial part, okay？ Time to test your boyfriend level.
Rinko wants to go to... Oh, you know what a boyfriend would do, right？
So, what do we do now？
Any idea what we're going to do now？
Where do we go first？ I'll leave it up to you.
Hey, what's the plan from here？
Where do you want to go？ Rinko doesn't mind going elsewhere...
What's next？ Come on, I'm waiting.
Next is... No, you have to decide.
So, where are we going to go next？
Any idea what to do next？ Don't leave Rinko hanging.
Hey, hey, what's next？ I can count on you, can't I？
It's hard to pick a movie, isn't it？ Rinko... wants to watch you like.
There are a lot of good ones out there. Which one do you want？
Which one shall I choose？ Oh, I should ask for my boyfriend's recommendation.
You're going to pick one of these？ You can choose whatever you like.
Which one do you want to see？ Tell me which one you like.
Which one do you want to watch？ Maybe I'd choose that one～.
None of the titles seem to have panned out.
Are they playing any good movies？
I have a favor to ask... Do you want another one？
You know what else sounds interesting？
Okay. Then let's see what else we can watch.
Hey, hey. Can I be a little selfish？
I might want to watch other movie...
I want to see other things too.
Don't you wish you could see at least one more film？
If you ask me, I'd like to see one more.
Isn't that good？ I think Rinko chose the same place.
Yeah. Sounds like fun. I'm all for it.
Nice. Rinko likes it there too.
Well, that's not bad, is it？
You know... Rinko's getting hungry. Do you want to go have lunch？
Let's go have lunch. Rinko has been hungry since a while ago.
I was hungry, too. Let's go then.
Rinko is hungry. I want to go somewhere.
Do you want to have lunch somewhere？
Aren't you hungry？ Let's go have lunch.
I'm so hungry I can't move. Hey, let's have dinner time, shall we？
Umm... why don't we have some tea and relax for a bit？
Rinko needs to rest. Can't we go somewhere to relax？
How about we have a some tea around here？ Rinko is a little tired.
I guess so. Let's take our time.
Is there a cafe or something？ I need to take a break.
Are you tired？ Let's take a break.
Hey, let's have tea. Rinko is a little tired.
I see. Then let's take a rest.
Rinko wants to have tea. Can't we？
Well... we're going to dinner, right？ I told you I didn't eat dinner today.
Of course. Let's go eat something good.
We're going to have dinner. I was planning on it.
Hey, do you want to go out for dinner？ Rinko told you she didn't have dinner today.
All right. Let's see where shall we eat.
It's getting late, do you want to go out for dinner？
That's true. No wonder I'm so hungry.
I'm getting hungry. Let's go eat somewhere.
I'm hungry, too. Let's go then.
This is the place, right？ Come on, let's go in.
We're here. Hurry up and get in.
I've arrived. Can we sit down？ Let's go in quickly.
We still have quite a bit of time, don't we？
Rinko doesn't want to leave yet.
At this time, Rinko may be able to play a little more.
Then we can go somewhere else.
I wonder if we can go to another place...
Hey. Let's go have fun somewhere else, shall we？
I see. Then let's play some more.
Yeah. That sounds good. So where do you want to go？
Right？ So, do you want to go play some more？
I agree, is there anywhere you want to go？
All right. Shall we play some more？
I get it, but if you're late, your parents at home will worry, right？
That's nice. Rinko has no complaints.
We don't have enough time to play there.
I'd love to go, but I don't think we have enough time...
You know... I'm not going to do it.
Why there...？ Hmm, I guess I'll just cancel...
I wonder why that place. You didn't get the message.
